column2:
imm[1:0]==3   shift simd32 mode:
shift_num = Value(Operand index 0)(0),   shifting low simds of val2 to the high simds of val1
Value(Operand index 2) = {Value(Operand index 2)(shift_num-1:0), Value(Operand index 1)(31:shift_num)}

imm==0:  
Val(Operand index 2) = Truncate( {Rx3,Rx2,Rx1,Rx0} )[7:0]  
imm==1:  
Val(Operand index 2)=Truncate( {Rx3(31),Rx2(31),Rx1(31),Rx0(31)},.., {Rx3(0),Rx2(0),Rx1(0),Rx0(0)} )[7:0]
       8bits*simd128              32bits*simd128 
用于QMADD后的TRCT8：
imm[1]=1: Rx0 => src2;
imm[2]=1: Rx1 => src2;
imm[3]=1: Rx2 => src2;
imm[4]=1: Rx3 => src2;
